---
title: Loaded Cheesy Lentil Nachos with Corn Salsa, Pickled Onion & Sour Cream
description: Get a load of this for a veggie masterpiece that looks just as amazing as it tastes! Crunchy tortilla wedges are piled high with a
cheese-topped lentil mix, corn salsa, sour cream, pickled onion and coriander.
